Create a card component


in the card class create a service class,router class,card.ts class.

Only a customer should be provided with this feature.[using of router after login]
It should allow to enter a new card details, details to be entered are,
Card Type: Can be Debit card or Credit card(should be selected from dropdown),(use drop down list)
Card number: Should be of 16 digits[maxlength,minlength]
CVV: Should be of 3 digits[maxlength,minlength]
Expiry Date: Only month and year should be entered, that should be of future.[use drop down list]
Name on Card: Only alphabets and spaces are allowed, the length should not be more than 50 characters, it should not contain only spaces.[pattern]
Note: The cvv should be hashed before storing to the database.
If all the validations are proper, the details should be stored to database.
Display proper messages in case of any error or exception.
